zoroaster.name: Zoroaster
zoroaster.bio: founder of Zoroastrianism, first to articulate monotheism

quasar.name: Quasar
quasar.bio: His ability to go with the flow let's him regulate the powers of a dangerous but power-giving belt he wears

pamReed.name: Pam Reed
pamReed.bio: In 2002 and 2003, Pam Reed was the overall winner (mens's and women's) of the Badwater Ultramarathon, a race from the continental United States' lowest elevation (in Death Valley) to (near) its highest elevation, a peak of 8000 ft.
